      "index": "aI",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "id": "p1_steps_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 310,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 3003,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1859421651,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784045621677,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Initial:  slow → 1,  fast → 1\n\nStep 1:   slow → 2  (moved 1),  fast → 3  (moved 2)\n\nStep 2:   slow → 3  (moved 1),  fast → 5  (moved 2)\n\nfast->next == NULL  →  STOP!\n\nslow is at node 3  →  ✅ That's the MIDDLE!",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "index": "aJ",
      "frameId": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Initial:  slow → 1,  fast → 1\n\nStep 1:   slow → 2  (moved 1),  fast → 3  (moved 2)\n\nStep 2:   slow → 3  (moved 1),  fast → 5  (moved 2)\n\nfast->next == NULL  →  STOP!\n\nslow is at node 3  →  ✅ That's the MIDDLE!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.0802469135802468
    },
    {
      "id": "p1_proof_title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 30,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 3010,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 2063447261,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784045621677,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Mathematical Proof:",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "index": "aK",
      "frameId": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Mathematical Proof:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.3636363636363635
    },
    {
      "id": "p1_proof_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 220,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ebfbee",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 40,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 3011,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 76174195,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784045621677,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "aL",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "id": "p1_proof_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 570,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 195,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 3012,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 512561469,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784045621677,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Let n = total number of nodes.\n\nIn each iteration:\n  • slow moves 1 step    → distance_slow = k  (after k iterations)\n  • fast moves 2 steps   → distance_fast = 2k (after k iterations)\n\nfast stops when it reaches the end:  2k = n  →  k = n/2\n\nAt that point, slow has moved k = n/2 steps.\n\nn/2 is exactly the middle index!   ∎\n\nFor even n: slow lands on the 2nd middle (standard convention).",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "index": "aM",
      "frameId": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Let n = total number of nodes.\n\nIn each iteration:\n  • slow moves 1 step    → distance_slow = k  (after k iterations)\n  • fast moves 2 steps   → distance_fast = 2k (after k iterations)\n\nfast stops when it reaches the end:  2k = n  →  k = n/2\n\nAt that point, slow has moved k = n/2 steps.\n\nn/2 is exactly the middle index!   ∎\n\nFor even n: slow lands on the 2nd middle (standard convention).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.9375
    },
