      "text": "m = distance from HEAD to CYCLE START\nk = distance from CYCLE START to MEETING POINT\nL = total length of the cycle\n(L - k) = distance from MEETING POINT back to CYCLE START (remaining cycle)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
